    },
    {
      "id": "843fe53a-a75e-4d11-9dd4-018d758e2beb",
      "type": "unit/page",
      "parentId": "f71d5f0e-7863-4ab6-8f24-1e1dea820bb5",
      "content": "<p>Binomial coefficient </p><p><math id=\"19121d25-963d-4c9a-89ac-93bc35870870\"></math></p><p> can be computed in this way: </p><code block=\"block\" lang=\"cpp\">int choose(int n, int k) {<br />  if (k &gt; n) return 0;<br />  if (k &gt; n - k) k = n - k;<br /><br />  int r = 1;<br />  for (int i = 1; i &lt;= k; i++)<br />    r = r * (n - k + i) / i;<br /><br />  return r;<br />}</code><p>For example, <code lang=\"cpp\">choose(4, 2);</code> returns 6.</p>"
    },
